br>\n          <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.3390/nu16040496\" target=\"_blank\">Ver estudio</a>\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"study-card\">\n        <p class=\"study-title\">L-Teanina</p>\n        <p class=\"study-reference\">\n          Chen, Q. et al. “L-Theanine increases longevity in C. elegans.”<br>\n          <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.3390/molecules29112691\" target=\"_blank\">Ver estudio</a>\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"study-card\">\n        <p class=\"study-title\">Sirtuinas</p>\n        <p class=\"study-reference\">\n          Sah, S. et al. “Sirtuin activators as geroprotectors.”<br>\n          <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.37349/eds.2025.100881\" target=\"_blank\">Ver estudio</a>\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"study-card\">\n        <p class=\"study-title\">Colina</p>\n        <p class=\"study-reference\">\n          Poly, C. et al. “Choline intake and cognitive performance.”<br>\n          <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.3945/ajcn.110.008938\" target=\"_blank\">Ver estudio</a>\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"study-card\">\n        <p class=\"study-title\">Vitamina K2</p>\n        <p class=\"study-reference\">\n          Mandatori, D. et al. “Vitamin K2, vascular health, and bone metabolism.”<br>\n          <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.3390/nu13041222\" target=\"_blank\">Ver estudio</a>\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"study-card\">\n        <p class=\"study-title\">Tiamina</p>\n        <p class=\"study-reference\">\n          Marrs, C. et al. “Thiamine deficiency and aging.”<br>\n          <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.3390/cells10102595\" target=\"_blank\">Ver estudio</a>\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"study-card\">\n        <p class=\"study-title\">Vitamina B12</p>\n        <p class=\"study-reference\">\n          Jatoi, N. et al. “Vitamin B12 and cognitive decline.”<br>\n          <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.7759/cureus.6976\" target=\"_bl